text: If you are looking for an affordable place to stay, this is definitely it. But you get what you pay for so don't expect a lot. There was a miscommunication with our rooms and the place had a roach when we came in. Wifi is free though.
Affordable accommodation with  WiFi, several bathrooms with soaps and shampoos, fridge with loaded bread and cereal, and of course washing machine and dryer. Great overall.
Best for economic visit with constrained budget!!!
Nice place, nice staff nice location.
